  "title": "HEAD BAKER",
  "description": "<p>Head Baker</p><p>Able to create new products and bring in feasible ideas to improve the existing products.</p><p>Cost effectiveness without conflicting with the quality and quantity.</p><p>Good time management to ensure smooth operations.</p><p>Ensure no disruption to production due to shortage of ingredients.</p><p>Able to lead and motivate the kitchen staffs. </p><p>Highest standard of cleanliness in the kitchen at all times.</p><p>Permanently night shift.</p><p>Must have knowledge with utensils and equipment maintenance.</p><p>Have at least five years of experience in the same field.</p>",
